17
00:02:45,942 --> 00:02:48,742
AS ONE OF THE 3 GREATEST
FENG SHUI MASTERS ON MARS,

18
00:02:48,742 --> 00:02:51,142
BUT WHEN I FINALLY
MANAGED TO LOCATE HIM,

19
00:02:51,142 --> 00:02:54,008
