COULDN'T SEND ME

21
00:03:01,075 --> 00:03:03,142
THAT MESSAGE
FROM HERE, COULD YOU?

22
00:03:03,142 --> 00:03:06,075
THE ONE WHO VISITS
FROM THE INAUSPICIOUS DOOR

