KNOWS ABOUT HIS ACCIDENT YET.

86
00:06:16,875 --> 00:06:20,042
"MESSAGE.
SEEK THE HOLY BEAST OF ANZAN

87
00:06:20,042 --> 00:06:23,075
I AM WHERE THE 4 GODS MEET."

88
00:06:23,075 --> 00:06:24,208
WHAT'S THIS?

89
00:06:24,208 --> 00:06:28,142
THIS IS A MESSAGE THAT WAS
SENT HERE BY YOUR FATHER.

90
00:06:28,142 --> 00:06:29,108
WHEN?

91
00:06:29,108 --> 00:06:30,908
3 DAYS AGO.

92
00:06:30,908 --> 00:06:33,942
RIGHT BEFORE THE ACCIDENT.

93
00:06:33,942 --> 00:06:37,275
