CAN YOU HELP ME, PLEASE?

94
00:06:37,275 --> 00:06:39,842
- HUH?
- IT HAS TO BE.

95
00:06:39,842 --> 00:06:41,275
IT'S ABOUT THE SUN STONE.

96
00:06:41,275 --> 00:06:42,308
SUN STONE? WHAT'S THAT?

97
00:06:42,308 --> 00:06:45,775
THE DIRECTION, THEY DAY,
AND THE TIME YOU ARRIVED

98
00:06:45,775 --> 00:06:48,342
WERE ALL THE BEST COMBINATION
FOR FENG SHUI,

99
00:06:48,342 --> 00:06:51,008
ESPECIALLY IF YOU'RE ON A QUEST.

100
00:06:51,008 --> 00:06:52,342
WHAT KIND OF QUEST?

101
00:06:52,342 --> 00:06:56,275
FOR THE SUN STONE.
PLEASE, JET, HELP ME.

102
00:06:56,275 --> 00:06:59,308
YES. YEAH, WE'LL HAVE IT SOON.

103
00:06:59,308 --> 00:07:01,975
RIGHT. I UNDERSTAND.
[HANGS UP TELEPHONE]

104
00:07:01,975 --> 00:07:03,275
SO HOW'S THE BOSS TAKING IT?

105
00:07:03,275 --> 00:07:06,375
AH, YOU KNOW.
THAT CAN'T BE REAL GOOD.

106
00:07:06,375 --> 00:07:09,408
NOT GOOD AT ALL.
LET'S DO IT.

107
00:07:09,408 --> 00:07:14,008
I DIDN'T OWE ANY FAVORS
TO PAO OR THE GIRL.

108
00:07:14,008 --> 00:07:16,008
I COULD'VE JUST
BLOWN THE WHOLE THING OFF,

109
00:07:16,008 --> 00:07:17,742
BUT SOMETHING MADE ME HANG ON.

110
00:07:17,742 --> 00:07:20,042
MAYBE IT WAS
ALL THE DANGLING QUESTIONS.

111
00:07:20,042 --> 00:07:22,842
WHY'D PAO SEND THE MESSAGE
TO ME BEFORE HE DIED?

112
00:07:22,842 --> 00:07:26,075
4 GODS AND THE HOLY BEAST
OF ANZAN.

113
00:07:26,075 --> 00:07:27,242
WHAT DID ALL THAT MEAN?

114
00:07:27,242 --> 00:07:28,875
AND WHO WERE THE GUYS

115
00:07:28,875 --> 00:07:30,942
WHO TRIED TO SHOOT
US AT THE GRAVESITE?

116
00:07:30,942 --> 00:07:32,742
AND THEN THERE WAS MEIFA,

117
00:07:32,742 --> 00:07:38,342
WITH HER GYPSY SCARF
AND ALL THAT SPIRIT.

118
00:07:38,342 --> 00:07:40,042
HMM.

119
00:07:51,708 --> 00:07:54,142
THE UNIVERSE IS
COMPOSED OF THE 3 CHIS.

120
00:07:54,142 --> 00:07:56,375
ONE IS THE CHI OF HEAVEN,

121
00:07:56,375 --> 00:07:58,875
THE ENERGY THAT
COMES FROM THE SUN,

122
00:07:58,875 --> 00:08:00,742
AND ONE IS THE CHI OF EARTH,

123
00:08:00,742 --> 00:08:04,308
THE POWER THAT COMES FROM
THE PLANET WE ALL LIVE ON,

124
00:08:04,308 --> 00:08:07,075
AND THE LAST ONE
IS THE MAGNETIC CHI

125
00:08:07,075 --> 00:08:10,042
THAT COMES FROM
LIVING ORGANISMS LIKE US.

126
00:08:10,042 --> 00:08:11,942
YOU MEAN, HUMAN CHI?

127
00:08:11,942 --> 00:08:13,408
YES, FROM THE HUMAN BODY.

128
00:08:13,408 --> 00:08:15,975
EACH BODY PRODUCES
A MAGNETIC FIELD,

129
00:08:15,975 --> 00:08:18,375
WHICH INTERACTS WITH
THE MAGNETIC FIELD OF THE EARTH,

130
00:08:18,375 --> 00:08:20,975
AND THAT'S WHAT CREATES
THE ENERGY WE ALL USE.

131
00:08:20,975 --> 00:08:21,708
UNIVERSAL FENG SHUI IS A SCIENCE

132
00:08:21,708 --> 00:08:25,442
THAT READS THESE
NATURAL ENERGIES

133
00:08:25,442 --> 00:08:28,942
AND APPLIES THEM
TO EVERYDAY LIFE.

134
00:08:31,942 --> 00:08:32,842
ICE CREAM.

135
00:08:32,842 --> 00:08:35,942
HUH? MMM! MMM.

136
00:08:35,942 --> 00:08:37,875
UNIVERSAL FENG SHUI.

137
00:08:37,875 --> 00:08:40,842
IS THAT ANY DIFFERENT
THAN PLAIN OLD FORTUNE TELLING?

138
00:08:40,842 --> 00:08:42,175
FORTUNE TELLING, INDEED.

139
00:08:42,175 --> 00:08:44,975
FORTUNE TELLERS
ONLY PREDICT AND FORESEE,

140
00:08:44,975 --> 00:08:45,975
BUT FENG SHUI IS ACTIVE.

141
00:08:45,975 --> 00:08:49,042
IT HAS THE POWER TO TURN
BAD LUCK INTO GOOD LUCK.

142
00:08:49,042 --> 00:08:50,375
FOR EXAMPLE, IF YOU
WERE A POWERFUL

143
00:08:50,375 --> 00:08:54,875
FENG SHUI MASTER
LIKE MY FATHER... OH.

144
00:08:54,875 --> 00:08:56,675
HMM? WHAT'S WRONG?

145
00:08:56,675 --> 00:09:01,442
I JUST REALIZED THAT
I NEVER SPENT ANY TIME LIKE THIS

146
00:09:01,442 --> 00:09:02,842
TALKING WITH MY FATHER.

147
00:09:02,842 --> 00:09:03,542
WAIT A MINUTE.

148
00:09:03,542 --> 00:09:04,942
FIRST OF ALL, I'M NOT OLD ENOUGH

149
00:09:04,942 --> 00:09:05,942
TO BE YOUR FATHER, ALL RIGHT?

150
00:09:05,942 --> 00:09:09,975
WHY, IF ANYTHING,
I COULD BE YOUR BOYFRIEND.

151
00:09:10,175 --> 00:09:13,208
NO, WAIT, THAT WOULD BE BAD,
WOULDN'T IT?

152
00:09:13,208 --> 00:09:15,975
OPEN FOOT, INSERT MOUTH.

153
00:09:15,975 --> 00:09:18,942
I MEAN, I'D BE MORE LIKE
YOUR OLDER BROTHER.

154
00:09:18,942 --> 00:09:20,442
ICE CREAM.

155
00:09:20,442 --> 00:09:22,875
ICE CREAM?
ICE CREAM CONE.

156
00:09:22,875 --> 00:09:27,675
HUH? OOH!
[GOBBLING]

157
00:09:27,675 --> 00:09:31,908
[LAUGHS]
LET'S GO, BIG BROTHER.

158
00:09:35,808 --> 00:09:39,142
I BELIEVE ANZAN
REFERS TO THIS BUILDING

159
00:09:39,142 --> 00:09:42,075
THE MOUNTAIN HOTEL.

160
00:09:43,275 --> 00:09:45,342
OVER THERE!

161
00:09:50,008 --> 00:09:51,275
AH...

162
00:09:51,275 --> 00:09:53,942
BLUE DRAGON.

163
00:10:01,875 --> 00:10:03,775
WHITE TIGER.

164
00:10:05,842 --> 00:10:07,875
SNAKE AND TORTOISE.

165
00:10:10,475 --> 00:10:11,708
RED PHOENIX!

166
00:10:11,708 --> 00:10:12,842
WHAT'S THAT?

167
00:10:12,842 --> 00:10:16,308
THE ZENITH CROSS.
IT'S THE 4 GODS.

168
00:10:22,842 --> 00:10:24,875
IT'S HERE.
IT'S THE SUN STONE.

169
00:10:24,875 --> 00:10:26,408
YOU SURE ABOUT THAT?

170
00:10:58,184 --> 00:10:59,717
UHH... HHH!

171
00:11:02,184 --> 00:11:04,050
- HHH... UHH!
- OOH, CAREFUL.

172
00:11:05,517 --> 00:11:09,484
