THIS IS IT, JET. THE SUN STONE.

173
00:11:09,484 --> 00:11:12,150
A BLACK ROCK?

174
00:11:12,150 --> 00:11:13,817
HUH?

175
00:11:21,084 --> 00:11:23,884
UH, JET, HEY!

176
00:11:28,117 --> 00:11:31,817
