177
00:11:32,084 --> 00:11:35,417
- GET OUTTA HERE.
- HEY! SKEEZERS. STUPID SUIT!

178
00:11:35,417 --> 00:11:39,817
A BOTTLE OF LAOCHU.
I DON'T NEED A GLASS.

179
00:11:46,850 --> 00:11:49,784
[PUNCHING] UHH!
HEY! OOH! AAH.

180
00:11:49,784 --> 00:11:54,950
HUH! HUH! UHH! UHH!
UHH! UHH! UHH! UHH!

181
00:11:54,950 --> 00:11:57,817
HUH? UHH? UHH. UHH.

182
00:11:57,817 --> 00:12:01,250
[GRR]
NOW, WHAT ARE YOU GUYS UP TO?

183
00:12:01,250 --> 00:12:04,017
HUH. YOU THINK
I'M GONNA TELL YOU THAT?

184
00:12:04,017 --> 00:12:04,817
NOT A CHANCE, BALDY.

185
00:12:04,817 --> 00:12:06,750
OOH
[MUFFLED SPEECH]

186
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:09,917
WE'RE FROM THE BLUE SNAKE.
WE'RE ON AN ASSIGNMENT

187
00:12:09,917 --> 00:12:11,850
SO YOU'RE SYNDICATE SCUMBAGS.

188
00:12:11,850 --> 00:12:13,750
WHAT ARE YOU
FOLLOWING US AROUND FOR?

189
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:15,750
I-I CAN'T TELL YOU THAT,

190
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:18,017
EVEN IF YOU KILL ME.
I CAN'T TELL YOU ANY MORE.

191
00:12:18,017 --> 00:12:19,750
[CHOKING]
IT'S PAO.

192
00:12:19,750 --> 00:12:22,717
WE WERE AFTER HIM,
BUT HE GOT AWAY.

193
00:12:22,717 --> 00:12:23,417
[GASPS]
[CHOKING]

194
00:12:23,417 --> 00:12:25,250
WE TRACKED THE MESSAGE HE SENT.

195
00:12:25,250 --> 00:12:26,484
THAT'S WHAT LED US TO YOU.

196
00:12:26,484 --> 00:12:28,917
[CHOKING]
I'M TELLING YOU THE TRUTH.

197
00:12:28,917 --> 00:12:30,250
WE'RE ON THE LOW END,

198
00:12:30,250 --> 00:12:32,750
SO THAT'S ALL
THE INFORMATION THEY GAVE US.

199
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:35,784
[CHOKING]
YEAH, I BELIEVE YOU.

200
00:12:35,784 --> 00:12:37,484
AAH!

201
00:12:37,484 --> 00:12:41,050
[CHILDREN LAUGHING]
LOOK AT THESE CHEESY GLASSES!

202
00:12:41,050 --> 00:12:43,817
JET.
HMM?

203
00:12:43,817 --> 00:12:47,950
MY FATHER. HE'S ALIVE?

204
00:12:49,317 --> 00:12:52,850
THE WORDS IN PAO'S MESSAGE
HAD LED US TO THE STONE,

205
00:12:52,850 --> 00:12:54,384
BUT DID THAT MEAN
PAO WAS STILL ALIVE?

206
00:12:54,384 --> 00:12:58,484
IT SEEMED HE WANTED US
TO HAVE THIS STONE, BUT WHY?

207
00:12:58,484 --> 00:13:00,717
WHAT WERE WE SUPPOSED
TO DO WITH IT?

208
00:13:00,717 --> 00:13:01,784
EVERY TIME WE SOLVED A MYSTERY,
IT JUST LED TO NEW ONES,

209
00:13:01,784 --> 00:13:06,984
DARKER AND MORE UNSETTLING
THAN THE ONES BEFORE,

210
00:13:06,984 --> 00:13:10,250
AND OUR ONLY CLUE
WAS THE STONE ITSELF.

211
00:13:10,250 --> 00:13:13,117
I DECIDED TO RUN SOME TESTS.

212
00:13:16,817 --> 00:13:17,950
[BEEPING]

213
00:13:17,950 --> 00:13:19,784
SO THIS IS A PIECE OF THE MOON

214
00:13:19,784 --> 00:13:21,884
FROM THAT GATE
ACCIDENT 50 YEARS AGO.

215
00:13:21,884 --> 00:13:24,050
FENG SHUI MASTERS
CALL IT THE SUN STONE.

216
00:13:24,050 --> 00:13:25,750
YOU SEE, ALL THE
TIMESPACE FLUCTUATIONS

217
00:13:25,750 --> 00:13:27,984
WERE ABSORBED BY THE STONE,

218
00:13:27,984 --> 00:13:29,884
CONDENSING A TREMENDOUS AMOUNT
OF ENERGY

219
00:13:29,884 --> 00:13:32,717
WHICH HAS BEEN
AMPLIFIED BY THE SUN.

220
00:13:32,717 --> 00:13:33,617
[MUNCH]

221
00:13:33,617 --> 00:13:35,750
LOOKS LIKE A PLAIN
OLD MOON ROCK TO ME,

222
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:36,817
YOU KNOW?
[COUGHING]

223
00:13:36,817 --> 00:13:40,250
HEY, HOW MUCH IS IT WORTH
IF YOU TRY TO SELL IT?

224
00:13:40,250 --> 00:13:41,250
ALL RIGHT.

225
00:13:41,250 --> 00:13:43,384
YOU TWO SMOKE OUTSIDE
IF YOU NEED TO SMOKE.

226
00:13:43,384 --> 00:13:47,084
WHAT? EXCUSE ME, BUT YOU
ALWAYS SMOKE IN HERE, JET.

227
00:13:47,084 --> 00:13:49,250
THIS IS NOW
A NON-SMOKING AREA.

228
00:13:49,250 --> 00:13:51,150
COME ON.
YOU'RE JOKING AROUND, RIGHT?

229
00:13:51,150 --> 00:13:54,450
DO I LOOK LIKE
I'M JOKING TO YOU?

230
00:13:54,450 --> 00:13:56,817
IT'S MY SHIP.

231
00:13:56,817 --> 00:13:59,384
[SHIP'S HORNS BLOWING]

232
00:14:04,150 --> 00:14:06,950
HUH? HUH? AHH!

233
00:14:06,950 --> 00:14:10,484
