TO DO WITH THIS SUN STONE?

234
00:14:10,484 --> 00:14:13,717
I DON'T KNOW.
I HAVE NO IDEA.

235
00:14:13,717 --> 00:14:17,884
MY FATHER HAD SOMETHING
IN MIND, BUT WHAT? HUH?

236
00:14:17,884 --> 00:14:20,350
[DOG PANTING]
HEY! COME HERE!

237
00:14:20,350 --> 00:14:23,017
EIN! WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

238
00:14:25,417 --> 00:14:28,984
HUH? AHH.

239
00:14:28,984 --> 00:14:30,417
THE LUOPAN.

240
00:14:30,417 --> 00:14:31,350
WHAT IS IT?

241
00:14:31,350 --> 00:14:33,884
IT CAN'T BE.
IT SHOULDN'T SPIN LIKE THAT.

242
00:14:33,884 --> 00:14:36,050
I TOOK THE MAGNET OFF.

243
00:14:36,050 --> 00:14:39,984
I SEE. I GET IT NOW.

244
00:14:39,984 --> 00:14:41,750
SO THAT'S THE POINT!

245
00:14:41,750 --> 00:14:43,084
HUH?

246
00:14:43,084 --> 00:14:44,717
WE CAN DO IT!

247
00:14:47,933 --> 00:14:50,000
[WHINING]

248
00:14:59,006 --> 00:15:00,606
YOU SEE, MY FATHER
HAS A SUN STONE AS WELL.

249
00:15:00,606 --> 00:15:03,005
THE 2 STONES RESONATE
TO ONE ANOTHER.

250
00:15:03,005 --> 00:15:06,139
IF WE FOLLOW THE ENERGY,
IT'LL LEAD US TO MY FATHER.

251
00:15:06,139 --> 00:15:09,239
SO THAT'S WHY PAO WANTED YOU
TO FIND THIS STONE.

252
00:15:09,239 --> 00:15:10,439
IT'S LIKE A BEACON.

253
00:15:10,439 --> 00:15:15,705
YES, BUT I DON'T KNOW WHY
HE SENT THAT MESSAGE TO YOU...

254
00:15:16,239 --> 00:15:20,039
AND NOT TO ME.

255
00:15:26,005 --> 00:15:27,739
UHH?

256
00:15:27,739 --> 00:15:32,472
[SINGING INDISTINCTLY]

257
00:15:34,605 --> 00:15:36,405
WHAT DO YOU THINK, SPIKE?

258
00:15:36,405 --> 00:15:37,639
THEY MAKE A GOOD COUPLE.

259
00:15:37,639 --> 00:15:40,239
I THINK IT'S
A DANGEROUS COMBINATION.

260
00:15:40,239 --> 00:15:41,272
AND WHY IS THAT?

261
00:15:41,272 --> 00:15:43,405
THE MORE RIGHTEOUS A GUY WAS
BACK IN HIS YOUTH,

262
00:15:43,405 --> 00:15:45,505
THE MORE LIKELY
HE IS TO FALL

263
00:15:45,505 --> 00:15:48,139
FOR SOME YOUNG THING
WHEN HE GETS OLDER.

264
00:15:48,139 --> 00:15:49,105
IS THAT RIGHT?

265
00:15:49,105 --> 00:15:53,139
DEFINITELY. MEN ARE
EXTREMELY PREDICTABLE.

266
00:15:53,405 --> 00:15:57,072
MY FATHER BELIEVED
IN UNIVERSAL FENG SHUI

267
00:15:57,072 --> 00:15:58,205
AND IN NOTHING ELSE.

268
00:15:58,205 --> 00:16:02,672
HE COULDN'T BELIEVE IN PEOPLE,
SO MY MOTHER LEFT HIM

269
00:16:02,672 --> 00:16:05,105
AND SHE TOOK ME WITH HER.

270
00:16:05,105 --> 00:16:07,105
THAT WAS 7 YEARS AGO.

271
00:16:07,105 --> 00:16:12,139
THE THING IS, I'M SURE THAT
HE COULD'VE FOUND ME.

272
00:16:12,139 --> 00:16:14,672
IT WOULDN'T HAVE BEEN
ALL THAT HARD, YOU KNOW?

273
00:16:14,672 --> 00:16:17,539
BUT HE NEVER TRIED ONCE
IN ALL THOSE YEARS.

274
00:16:17,539 --> 00:16:20,105
I'M SURE THERE'S
A GOOD REASON FOR IT.

275
00:16:20,105 --> 00:16:22,005
AND WHAT'S THE REASON

276
00:16:22,005 --> 00:16:24,072
WHY THOSE MEN WERE
AFTER MY FATHER?

277
00:16:24,072 --> 00:16:24,972
HMM.

278
00:16:24,972 --> 00:16:27,039
THEY'RE BAD MEN!
HOW DID THEY KNOW HIM?

279
00:16:27,039 --> 00:16:30,572
PLEASE, TELL ME THE TRUTH, JET.

280
00:16:30,572 --> 00:16:33,947
I WANT TO KNOW WHO
MY FATHER REALLY IS.

281
00:16:37,305 --> 00:16:42,039
PAO WAS A CONSULTANT
FOR A MAJOR SYNDICATE.

282
00:16:42,039 --> 00:16:43,439
THAT'S THE REAL STORY.

283
00:16:43,439 --> 00:16:46,105
HE LEAKED SOME
INSIDE INFORMATION TO ME

284
00:16:46,105 --> 00:16:49,039
BACK WHEN I WAS A DETECTIVE
WITH I.S.S.P.

285
00:16:49,039 --> 00:16:50,205
SEE, HE WAS LOOKING
FOR A WAY OUT,

286
00:16:50,205 --> 00:16:52,039
AND HE THOUGHT I COULD
HELP HIM FIND IT.

287
00:16:52,039 --> 00:16:55,739
I TRIED, BUT IT'S IMPOSSIBLE
FOR SOMEONE TO LEAVE

288
00:16:55,739 --> 00:16:56,805
WHEN THEY KNOW THAT MUCH.

289
00:16:56,805 --> 00:16:59,439
ONCE YOU JOIN A SYNDICATE,
THEY OWN YOU FOREVER.

290
00:16:59,439 --> 00:17:01,005
IF YOU CROSS THEM,

291
00:17:01,005 --> 00:17:05,105
THEY TAKE REVENGE ON
YOU AND YOUR FAMILY.

292
00:17:05,105 --> 00:17:08,139
I'M SURE THAT'S WHAT
HE WAS TRYING TO AVOID.

293
00:17:08,139 --> 00:17:08,939
OH...

294
00:17:08,939 --> 00:17:11,239
THINK YOU CAN
ASK HIM YOURSELF,

295
00:17:11,239 --> 00:17:14,672
IF THE SUN STONE
LEADS US TO HIM.

296
00:17:22,639 --> 00:17:27,672
AHH. YEAH, YEAH, YEAH, YEAH...

297
00:17:27,672 --> 00:17:32,039
HERE. OVER THIS WAY.

298
00:17:37,639 --> 00:17:41,405
THERE'S NOTHING HERE.
AND THE RADAR?

299
00:17:41,405 --> 00:17:42,272
UHUH.

300
00:17:42,272 --> 00:17:43,272
THAT CAN'T BE.

301
00:17:43,272 --> 00:17:46,139
I'M SURE THIS IS
THE RIGHT SPOT.

302
00:17:46,139 --> 00:17:47,305
HMM?

303
00:17:47,305 --> 00:17:50,339
[PINGING]
WAIT. HOLD ON.

304
00:17:54,105 --> 00:17:54,972
GOT COMPANY.

305
00:17:54,972 --> 00:17:56,639
THESE GUYS NEVER GIVE UP.

306
00:17:56,639 --> 00:17:57,605
SPIKE, FAYE, DEPLOY.

307
00:17:57,605 --> 00:18:01,972
THIS IS YOUR LITTLE PARTY, JET.
[EXPLOSION]

308
00:18:01,972 --> 00:18:04,205
BATTLESTATIONS OR
DIE WITH THE SHIP.

309
00:18:04,205 --> 00:18:06,205
THOSE ARE YOUR OPTIONS.

310
00:18:11,105 --> 00:18:12,272
WHAT THE HELL AM I
DOING THIS FOR?

311
00:18:12,272 --> 00:18:16,105
IT'S CALLED GIVING, FAYE.
THINK OF US AS FAIRY GODPARENTS.

312
00:18:16,105 --> 00:18:20,105
WE'RE ABOUT TO GRANT THE
PRINCESS A VERY SPECIAL WISH.

313
00:18:20,105 --> 00:18:21,539
WE ARE, HUH?

314
00:18:27,172 --> 00:18:28,005
[BEEPING]
ROBOT SHIPS?

315
00:18:28,005 --> 00:18:32,272
SO THESE MUST BE
THE EVIL STEPSISTERS.

316
00:18:35,205 --> 00:18:37,005
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

317
00:18:37,005 --> 00:18:38,105
THEY'RE TRYING TO SCARE US.

318
00:18:38,105 --> 00:18:40,439
I GOT IT!
I GOT IT! I GOT IT!

319
00:18:46,705 --> 00:18:49,072
UHH.

320
00:18:53,272 --> 00:18:55,705
- SPIKE! COME BACK IN.
- WHAT'S THAT?

321
00:18:55,705 --> 00:18:58,372
NEW PLAN.
LOOKS LIKE IF WE APPLY

322
00:18:58,372 --> 00:18:59,372
ENOUGH ENERGY TO THE SUN STONE,

323
00:18:59,372 --> 00:19:02,172
WE CAN DRAW OUT THE FORCES
TRAPPED INSIDE IT.

324
00:19:02,172 --> 00:19:04,039
YEAH? GREAT. THEN WHAT?

325
00:19:04,039 --> 00:19:07,672
THEN WE TAKE OUR SHOT.
ALL OR NOTHING.

326
00:19:12,472 --> 00:19:15,672
WHATEVER YOU'RE GONNA DO,
DO IT FAST.

327
00:19:18,139 --> 00:19:18,705
I PUT IT IN.

328
00:19:18,705 --> 00:19:21,972
ALL RIGHT.
[BUZZING]

329
00:19:24,405 --> 00:19:27,405
SPIKE, HIT IT
WITH YOUR PLASMA CANNON.

330
00:19:27,405 --> 00:19:31,105
RIGHT, I'M SHOOTING
A ROCK NOW.

331
00:20:23,105 --> 00:20:25,272
[BEEPING]
HUH?

332
00:20:27,705 --> 00:20:30,205
LOOKS LIKE YOU MADE IT
IN TIME, JET.

333
00:20:30,205 --> 00:20:31,005
[GASPS]

334
00:20:31,005 --> 00:20:33,005
PAO. YOU'RE ALIVE.

335
00:20:33,005 --> 00:20:36,372
MEIFA, IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME.

336
00:20:36,372 --> 00:20:38,172
[GASPS]

337
00:20:43,072 --> 00:20:46,172
PAO, YOU'RE IN
AN UNSTABLE FORCE FIELD.

338
00:20:46,172 --> 00:20:47,172
I CAN'T GET ANY CLOSER.

339
00:20:47,172 --> 00:20:52,405
YES, I KNOW. THERE'S NO
OXYGEN LEFT HERE ANYWAY.

340
00:20:52,405 --> 00:20:53,272
[GASPS]

341
00:20:53,272 --> 00:20:56,472
I SENT YOU THAT MESSAGE
BECAUSE I HOPED

342
00:20:56,472 --> 00:20:59,739
YOU'D MANAGED TO BRING
MY DAUGHTER OUT HERE.

343
00:20:59,739 --> 00:21:02,539
IN OTHER WORDS, YOU'RE SAYING
YOU USED FENG SHUI

344
00:21:02,539 --> 00:21:06,505
TO REACH US AND BRING US
OUT HERE ACCORDING TO YOUR WILL.

345
00:21:06,505 --> 00:21:09,105
THAT'S RIGHT.

346
00:21:16,739 --> 00:21:18,139
IT'S NOT RIGHT.

347
00:21:18,139 --> 00:21:20,672
YOU WEREN'T IN CONTROL
OF THIS OPERATION.

348
00:21:20,672 --> 00:21:26,286
MEIFA IS HERE NOW BECAUSE
BECAUSE SHE WANTED TO FIND YOU.

349
00:21:27,205 --> 00:21:30,739
HUH. YOU MIGHT BE RIGHT.

350
00:21:30,739 --> 00:21:35,272
PERHAPS I GAVE MYSELF
TOO MUCH CREDIT.

351
00:21:37,205 --> 00:21:42,647
MEIFA, IT'S SO WONDERFUL
TO SEE YOU ONE LAST TIME.

352
00:21:43,405 --> 00:21:47,739
I HATED YOU.
I HATED YOU FOR ALL THOSE YEARS.

353
00:21:47,739 --> 00:21:53,139
IT'S TRUE.
IT HURT SO MUCH.

354
00:21:56,139 --> 00:21:59,205
BUT NOW I DON'T.

355
00:22:08,139 --> 00:22:10,072
DADDY.

356
00:22:20,272 --> 00:22:24,705
NOW, I DON'T KNOW IF IT WAS
A GOOD THING OR A BAD THING

357
00:22:24,705 --> 00:22:26,572
THAT WE BROUGHT HER OUT THERE,

358
00:22:26,572 --> 00:22:30,739
BUT THAT WAS HOW
THIS PECULIAR CASE ENDED.

359
00:22:30,739 --> 00:22:33,372
MEIFA WENT BACK HOME TO MARS,

360
00:22:33,372 --> 00:22:36,972
OUR NO SMOKING AREA
BECAME A SMOKING ZONE AGAIN,

361
00:22:36,972 --> 00:22:42,039
AND LIFE RETURNED TO THE SAME
DAILY ROUTINE, JUST LIKE BEFORE.

362
00:22:42,039 --> 00:22:44,239
ONE THING HAS CHANGED, THOUGH.

363
00:22:44,239 --> 00:22:45,439
WHEN I READ THE NEWS,

364
00:22:45,439 --> 00:22:47,472
I NEVER CHECK
THE HOROSCOPES ANYMORE.

365
00:24:28,605 --> 00:24:31,972
HE CAME WITH A WHISTLE.

366
00:24:37,772 --> 00:24:41,605
AND HE APPEARED OUT OF
THE BLUE ON HORSEBACK.

367
00:24:41,605 --> 00:24:43,672
WHO IS HE?

368
00:24:43,672 --> 00:24:46,705
FRIEND OR FOE, OR JUST
AN OLDFASHIONED COWPOKE?

369
00:24:46,705 --> 00:24:49,539
THE NEXT EPISODE
IS A SHOCKING SCIFI

370
00:24:49,539 --> 00:24:51,605
SPAGHETTI-WESTERN EPIC SAGA.

371
00:24:51,605 --> 00:24:53,205
"COWBOY FUNK."

372
00:24:53,205 --> 00:24:56,405
HEY, ARE WE TAKING THIS
COWBOY THING A LITTLE TOO FAR?

